reviews.review_text: Red Rocks 1985 ~ AYFKM!! Red Rocks was/is always sprecial. And 1985 was a great year for the Dead IMHO. They were not always right on, but many nights the energy was extremely high. This is one of those nights - place & time intersection. Oh to turn back time and be a head in the crowd at Red Rocks on Sept. 7th, 1985.  God bless them and all those who truly love them~!
It was a Grate one This last of 3 shows in 1985 was the last time I was at Red Rocks. Flaws and flubs aside, there was energy and passion flowing. You can hear it in this matrix.
